<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. تَرَنَّمَ فِي مِحْرَابِهِ مُتَمَايِلِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَمُدُّ يَدَيْهِ سَائِلاً مُتَضَرِّعًا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>لِرَبٍّ قَرِيبٍ بِالإِجَابَةِ كَافِلِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَجَاءَتْ سِهَامُ اللَّيْلِ تَهْوِي بِسُرْعَةٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>إلى ظَالِمٍ عَنْ ظُلْمِهِ مُتَغَافِلِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَصَابَتْ نِيَاطَ الْقَلْبِ فِي وَسْطِ نَحْرِهِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَآبَ بِخَسْرَانٍ وَحَرِّ بِلابِلِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَقُمْ قَارِعًا لِلْبَابِ وَالنَّابِ نَادِمًا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>عَلَى مَا جَرَى وَأَقْبَلَ عَلَيْهِ وَسَائِلِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَأَمَّا بَنُو الدُّنْيَا فَلا تَرْج نَفْعَهُمْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَلا مُرْتَقَى مِنْهُمْ يُرْجَى لِنَازِلِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَإِنِّي تَتَبعْتُ الأَنَامَ فَلَمْ أَجِدْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>سِوَى حَاسِدٍ أَوْ شَامِتٍ أَوْ مُعَاذِلِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَلَمْ أَرَى أَنْكَى لِلْعَدُوِّ مِنَ الدُّعَا<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>كَرَمِي بِنَبْلٍ أُوتِرَتْ بِالْمَنَاصِلِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَلا تَدْعُ غَيْرَ اللهِ فِي كُلِّ حَالَةٍ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَخَلِّ جَمِيعَ الْخَلْقِ طُرًا وَعَازِلِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>سَأَلْتُكَ يَا ذَا الْجُودِ وَالْمَنِّ وَالْعَطَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>تَجُودُ وَتَعْفُو عَنْ عُبَيْدِكَ يَا وَلِي<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَتُرْسِلَ طَاعُونًا وَرِجْزًا وَنِقْمَةً<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَطَعْنًا لِطَعَّانِ وَقَتْلاً لِقَاتِلِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>